title: Red Revival- Winning with a Swiftness (Nicole's Version)
description:
We have one last thing to do before we wrap up this Red era, and that's to hook up one of the best Swifties! Meet Nicole, and let us know if you have any song suggestions for this sweet blushing bride!
Thank you for your support, Nicole! We are so honored to have you in our Swiftie squad!
